show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Iris Turner is a rich lady. Iris gets lost and loses her memory when she’s a kid. She’s adopted and becomes the master of Eternity Pavilion. Then, Iris is betrayed and hurt badly. Kayden Ford saves her but abandons her later. Iris finds her brothers and exposes Kayden. Kayden fails to make a comeback. Fiona Wood holds Iris is dating Iris’s third brother, so Fiona tries to get revenge. Iris stops her, and the Wood family goes bankrupt. Iris and her brothers live happily ever after.
